overview:
The Warehouse of Online IT Support And Services.

ImGuni computer technical support has a wide range of services wherein they provide assistance with technology products such as computers, software, modem, router, printer, scanner and any product connected with PC. In general, they help the user to solve specific problems with a product along with providing basic training of pc usage, customization or other support services.

ImGuni is the Online Computer Technical Support and Services organization, making sure that the customers are treated with utmost priority and care. They have highly skilled and trained Microsoft Certified Professionals, Cisco certified professionals and Backup and Recovery experts, who strive hard to resolve each and every query of the customer.

Here is the glimpse of some of the services that Imguni provides : Virus diagnosis, virus removal, PC Tune-up, ID theft protection, email account setup, software installation, printer setup, computer troubleshooting, network setup, wireless setup, ISP support and many more.

ImGuni Online Computer Technical support may be delivered over the telephone, online, chat or by E-mail. Technician log a call/ incident so that if the issue persists than it can be taken to next level rather than starting whole thing again.
